In adjudicating a waiver request, I would like evidence that granting the request is compatible with NJCU’s promise to teach the students what they need for a successful personal life, civic life, and professional life. To that end, please answer the following questions:
Why has the student not satisfied the relevant requirement(s) to date?

In adjudicating a waiver request, I would like evidence that granting the request is compatible with NJCU’s promise to teach the students what they need for a successful personal life, civic life, and professional life. To that end, please answer the following questions:
Why has the student not satisfied the relevant requirement(s) to date?
Why is the student unable to satisfy the relevant requirement(s) in a future semester?
What other options have been explored to ensure the student can satisfy the requirement(s)?
